H3.text: Kirkland Signature is the house brand of what retail giant. Costco

A4.text: Kirkland Signature is Costco's private label brand, featured on a wide array of products sold across Costco's warehouses and its website.

A5.text: Costco Wholesale Corporation, doing business as Costco, is an American multinational corporation which operates a chain of membership-only big-box warehouse club retail stores.
